snippet.title: Future Update Sneak Peek: Space Combat in LandRocker's Liberation Mode
snippet.description:
Catch a glimpse of the future with LandRocker's Liberation Mode: intense fighter rover battles against enemy ships in space! This sneak peek reveals thrilling space combat, showcasing advanced fighter rovers equipped with powerful weaponry engaging in high-stakes encounters. More updates on this exhilarating feature are coming soon!

About LandRocker
LandRocker is a P2E game about discovery and space exploration. As a brave and resourceful player, you'll journey to faraway planets, launching exhilarating mining missions to collect rare and valuable resources such as NFTs, crypto tokens, and crafting materials.
